AI Video Assistant

An AI-powered meeting intelligence system that automatically transcribes, summarizes, and lets users chat with meeting recordings using RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation). Supports YouTube videos, MP3, MP4, and WAV files with multilingual transcription for English, Hindi, and Hinglish.

🚀 Features
🎙️ Upload audio/video files or paste YouTube URLs
🧠 Automatic meeting transcription using Whisper AI
🌍 Hindi & Hinglish transcription support with Sarvam AI
📝 AI-generated meeting summaries in bullet points
✅ Extracts action items, key decisions, and follow-ups
💬 Chat with your meeting using RAG + ChromaDB
📄 Export reports as PDF or TXT
⚡ Fully local AI pipeline with minimal API cost

🛠️ Tech Stack
Category	Technologies
Language	Python
Frontend	Streamlit
AI Models	OpenAI Whisper, Mistral AI, Sarvam AI
RAG Framework	LangChain LCEL
Vector Database	ChromaDB
Embeddings	HuggingFace Embeddings
Audio Processing	yt-dlp, FFmpeg
Export	fpdf2


🏗️ System Architecture
YouTube/File Input
        ↓
 Audio Processing (yt-dlp + FFmpeg)
        ↓
 Speech-to-Text (Whisper / Sarvam AI)
        ↓
 Meeting Summarization (Mistral AI)
        ↓
 Embeddings Generation
        ↓
 ChromaDB Vector Storage
        ↓
 RAG-based Chat System
        ↓
 PDF/TXT Export


